{"tid":1181052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"淨化耳朵！IU歌迷推薦最適合睡前聆聽的9首歌曲大公開","createTime":"2019-06-01T10:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T12:13:38.000Z","uid":34643,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"66367410385009832292aeda7b0079f97f56609c","tid":1181052,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"IU出道以來真的唱過太多好歌啦！最近韓國網友就從這茫茫星海中挑出了最適合睡前聽的9首歌曲，快加入睡前播放列表吧！<br />\n<br />\n1.《Ugly Duckling》<br />\n收錄於IU的出道迷你專輯《Lost and Found》，15歲IU的聲音，即便過去了10多年，仍然帶給人莫大的感動：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NRp7WTGNpIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNRp7WTGNpIU&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=1f1a305b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NRp7WTGNpIU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.《Knees》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1JUfCyeT5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL1JUfCyeT5E&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=91687e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1JUfCyeT5E</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.《夜信》<br />\n《Palette》的第一首先行曲，歌詞和旋律都非常優美：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzYnNdJhZQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBzYnNdJhZQw&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=da07ea85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzYnNdJhZQw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.《With A Determined Heart To Forget You》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZXmoJu81e6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZXmoJu81e6A&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=52763457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZXmoJu81e6A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.《Rain Drop》<br />\n收錄於第三張單曲《嘮叨》，幾乎是「藏」在角落了XD但其實也是很好聽的一首歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SXNgoMHqKAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSXNgoMHqKAc&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=ffee685e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SXNgoMHqKAc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.《My old story》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A6A_s_3ciVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA6A_s_3ciVs&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=3f7d2a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A6A_s_3ciVs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.《A Dreamer》<br />\n收錄於2009年首張正規專輯《Growing Up》，在灰暗現實中仍懷抱夢想的少女心聲真的十分感人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-CcnXf-X08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw-CcnXf-X08&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=f5f6290d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-CcnXf-X08</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8.《秘密》<br />\n收錄於2011年正規二專《Last Fantasy》，每次聽都讓人感歎根本是天使的聲音啊：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GMC389I3Es4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGMC389I3Es4&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=bcc7cc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GMC389I3Es4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.《仲夏夜之夢》<br />\n這首歌來自IU的首張翻唱專輯《花書簽》，2014年發行，到現在都是經典之一呀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gWAAdVS9Emg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgWAAdVS9Emg&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=2319261b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gWAAdVS9Emg</a>"},{"pid":"f0e081c6049bebd4efca64e43d7fcbb73c7f571b","tid":1181052,"uid":76632,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"訓醒起身再